channel.description:
i added an npc to my auto spawn list, and now when i log in, itlogs out and says in still logged in, i have pimpscape, help would be awsome
i compiled with no errors but bam this happend
heres what my runserver said [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img247.imageshack.us/img247/9633/yepvi8.png[/img][/URL]

item.title: I added an npc to Auto spawn in pimpscape.. now my servers broked
item.dc:creator: @Palidino76 Palidino76
item.description:
@Palidino76 wrote:

the format is this:
spawn = npcId[TAB]spawnX[TAB]spawnY[TAB]height[TAB]range1X[TAB]range1Y[TAB]range2X[TAB]rang2Y[TAB]walkType[TAB]any text here

all the x’s and y’s should probly be 4 numbers long (1234), the height normally 0, the walk type doesn’t matter because its been removed from non old servers, and most people put the npcs name at any text here or some kind of idetification
